long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Gitsnackhub is a browser extension for Chrome that lets you convert GitHub contribution chart to a game board and play snake game on it.

How to Active?
1. Open a github profile page. 
2. Double-click the last cell in the legend.

How to Play?
1. Use arrow ↑↓←→ to move.
2. Use SPACE to reset game while game over.

Source Code: https://github.com/sumy7/gitsnackhub

If you have any question, please open an issue from Github.
